Installing the AIS Proxy Server tool.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

BUILDING THE SOFTWARE
REQUIREMENTS
NOTES

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

BUILDING THE SOFTWARE

1) Type `./configure' at the system prompt. On some systems you may have to
   type `sh configure.'

2a) Type `make' to build the software.

2b) Optionally run the tests using `make check.' You'll need the DejaGNU
    package to run the tests.

3a) Install the ais_tool server component and the cgi script nph-ais in
    DODS_ROOT/etc by running `make install.'

REQUIREMENTS

  o You need to have the DAP library and at least libcurl, libz and librx from
    the third-party packages installed before building this software.

NOTES

